    "name": "Bumpstick",
    "steam_appid": 1750010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750010/extras/86dcbc5af4bda7dcc65a79a9f0fa5538.avif?t=1699410094\" width=580 height=180 /></span><br><br>Take control of your neon stick and bounce through the levels as fast as you can!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> fight for the best time in online leaderboards<br></li><li> unlock new customization options for your Bumpstick<br></li><li> save your favorite replays</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750010/extras/1.GIF?t=1699410094\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750010/extras/f4da5e58b32a0d884a52874b54f0c6f0.avif?t=1699410094\" width=580 height=180 /></span><br><br>There are a bunch of different obstacles. Use them to your advantage!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> glide with the wind<br></li><li> shoot yourself from &quot;cannons&quot;<br></li><li> slide on rails<br></li><li> and more!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750010/extras/2.GIF?t=1699410094\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750010/extras/a81ac1d3a4860bb7297cd8287bf512b2.avif?t=1699410094\" width=580 height=180 /></span><br><br>Bumpstick supports local multiplayer for as many people, as you can fit in front of the screen!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> set up the looks of each player<br></li><li> fight for the first place<br></li><li> play in special PvP game modes</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750010/extras/3.GIF?t=1699410094\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750010/extras/dc2b3f0677e79127c043a9e321692c8b.avif?t=1699410094\" width=580 height=180 /></span><br><br>Have a cool idea for a level? You can create it using the same editor that was used to create all the levels in the game and post it to the <strong>Steam Workshop</strong>, so others can play it too!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> play on levels created by other players<br></li><li> create your own ones and share them</li></ul>",
